  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    JNCC Interim CEO appointed
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Gemma Harper has been appointed as the Interim Chief Executive of JNCC following an open competition. </p>

  </div>
</div>

